name: $eq
desc: the value for the parameter in the resource is not equal to the provided value

name: $ne
desc: the value for the parameter in the resource is greater than the provided value

name: $gt
desc: the value for the parameter in the resource is less than the provided value

name: $lt
desc: the value for the parameter in the resource is greater or equal to the provided value

name: $ge
desc: the value for the parameter in the resource is less or equal to the provided value

name: $le
desc: the value for the parameter in the resource starts after the provided value

name: $sa
desc: the value for the parameter in the resource ends before the provided value

name: $eb
desc: the value for the parameter in the resource is approximately the same to the provided value.
